Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HADORRA VERUS BARAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Iora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begira--{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is too difficult!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't win like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begiragon!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Defending with Dragonic Auras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran has realized that Hadorra's body\Ncontains a Black Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mystban.\NHadorra may actually have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The attacks and spells\Nof Dragon Knights are too powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and will most likely detonate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fear of that keeps them\Nfrom fighting at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you holding back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the mighty Dragon Knights\Nhave lost their nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be because\Nyou're not used to fighting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran! Where's your Gigabrake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you too! Don't you want\Nto avenge your dead master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to take revenge on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! Hadorra doesn't know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe if I tell him, he'll stop fighting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hadorra! You've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mustn't tell him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! Why not?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Black Core can be detonated\Nby its creator's Magic Power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once Hadorra notices the Black Core,\NBan will detonate it on the spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll do it to stop Hadorra\Nfrom revolting against him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be fine. If we focus all our energy\Non defense, we should survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But your friends on the surface\Nare certain to perish!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you holding back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How very suspicious. What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up to nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gigaden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We were merely holding back\Nto analyze the extent of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, I shall face you\Nwith my ultimate blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you were just testing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a risk, but I have no choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to have him explode here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I decapitate him,\Nhe shouldn't detonate right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It should take a moment\Nfor Ban to detonate him, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I'll use all of my\NDragonic Aura to contain the blast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a crazy idea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't know if it can be contained\Nby a Dragonic Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's way too dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}do you trust me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I trust your strength\Nmore than anyone's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A good answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I trust your strength, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing you fight that Royal Guard member\Nand Hadorra, I realized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're far stronger than\Nwhen you fought me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You impress me with how you've grown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is something only I can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only with my sword skills\Nand abundance of Dragonic Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I need you to trust me here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get your friends out of here just in case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take that hole to the surface.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what happens to me\NI promise I'll take care of Hadorra!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I leave the fight with Ban to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise me you'll win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For you and for those who believe in you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What impressive power we wield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your Ultimate Blade, Gigabrake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have my Ultra Combustion Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Both infuse our blades\Nwith supercharged energy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to unleash at the moment of impact\Nand destroy our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nthe first to land a hit wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all be decided by the timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither of us require a second strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of our attacks\Nare strong enough to end things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe... I should help out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe using my Dragonic Aura\Nto help contain the blast...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't interfere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra's right. The timing is everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you interfere,\Nit increases my chances of failing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-But...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you say you trust my strength?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once Popp and the others are safe,\NI'll come back to help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise me you won't fail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise I'll be fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here I go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra! It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the true power of a Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gigabrake!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ultra Combustion Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! It didn't cut through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.61,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino! Hang in there, Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! The wound is too deep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Untreated, it could be fatal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You mean me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange. Your Gigabrake\Nwas much stronger when you fought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Why is my head\Nstill attached to my body?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran attacked at the perfect range\Nfor a fatal blow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I take a fatal blow\Nfrom Dragon Master General Baran{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and still have my head on my shoulders?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be pretty sad if a reaper\Nwas killed. Of course I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! The undying man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be alive\Nafter I cleaved you in half?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Cleaving me in half\Nwas the problem, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood in my veins has the same\Ncomposition as Underworld magma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super-hot and contains\Na powerful acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You went and cut me in half{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}getting my blood all over\Nyour Demon Dragon Blade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood corroded your sword,\Ndulling its sharpness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Demon Dragon Blade\Ncan't regenerate that damage quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Against someone as strong as Hadorra here,\Nit loses its effectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my curse, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A reaper always kills its target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You may evade me,\Nbut there are consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you have it, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'd like me taking your prey,\Nso I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to take care of Baran for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were ordered\Nto assassinate Baran, Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's a mystery with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an ugly wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Piroro, heal him will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll heal momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn to accept\Npeople's generosity, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as Baran dies,\Nmy job will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.\NI'd advise against showing any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should crush them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You may want a fair fight, but his sword\Nwon't regenerate for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that sort of time left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! It's all healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's another small wound here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're backing down\Nnot so that Hadorra can have the glory,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but to avoid the Black Core's explosion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye and good luck, Hadorra.\NYou too, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer not to win a fight\Nwith the Reaper's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have the luxury of waiting\Nuntil you're both ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be holding back, Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! If I stop the healing spell now,\NDino might not survive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let go of him,\Nno matter what attack comes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you choose\Nto protect your son. So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't extend this fight any longer!\NI must finish things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me and keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ionazun!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You fool! How could you be so reckless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm already fully healed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending! Your wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All this covering for each other\Nand walking on eggshells while fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're family aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to fight together,\Nlet's really fight together as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of us seriously work together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can find some new,\Nfinal power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A final power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Here goes, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an unlimited willpower he possesses!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai. Who gave that name to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Grampa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I washed up on Dermline Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My crib.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a name plate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the "D" was left on it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grampa gave me this name\Nso that at least...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd share the initial\Nmy real parents gave me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast the Sleep Spell Rarihoma on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the fighting to me and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie still and you should heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Dragon Knight.\NYour healing abilities should be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! H-How could you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Children may wish otherwise,\Nbut this is what parents must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dai," is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a good name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I hope you'll remember the name\Nthat Soara and I gave you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dino." In the Arukido Kingdom language\Nit means, "Strong Dragon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why does everybody do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Master... Even Master\Ncast Asutoron on me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So Aban did the same sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that, in the very end,\Npart of me learned how to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on! Good night, Dino!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go to sleep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dino?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep, Dino. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you never get the hang\Nof putting him to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like you're right, Soara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never got the hang\Nof putting him to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a parent at heart, Baran.\NYou risk yourself for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore I'd never use\Nthis power again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I use it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't put Dino to sleep\Nout of fear for his well being!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I once took this terrible form\Nwhen we battled before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want him to see it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That form! The Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So you plan to fight in\Nthe Dragon Knight's ultimate battle mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Die Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go to hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle against\Nthe Hadorra Royal Guard begins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in Ban Palace,\NBaran has put Dai to sleep{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and once again becomes the Dragonoid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the attack against his son,\NBaran unleashes his fury on Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban calmy watches\Nthe battle from his throne.{\i0}
